      <h1 class="ip-title">About LeavingAmerica.co</h1>
      <p class="ip-lead">LeavingAmerica.co is a free Salary Arbitrage calculator built for Americans who are curious about what life could look like abroad. Whether you are a remote worker exploring options, someone planning early retirement, or simply wondering if the grass is greener somewhere else, this tool gives you real numbers to work with.</p>
